author: Daisuke Wakabayashi
title: Apple’s Latest Challenge: Topping Its Own Success
text:
As Apple Inc. prepares to introduce its latest iPhones next week, the company’s biggest challenge is one of its making: how to top its own success.
Apple’s bigger-screen iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus, introduced a year ago, reignited sales growth for Apple’s smartphone, propelled the company to record profits and solidified Apple’s standing...
